furicam (1.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Port to Camera2 NDK API for full manual sensor control
  * HDR burst capture with manual-exposure bracketing (OpenCV Mertens fusion)
  * Fix AE lock: do not lock auto-exposure on tap-to-focus
  * Fix JPEG capture resolution always using max sensor size
  * Zoom slider with 0.1× steps and direct-ratio model
  * DNG/RAW capture pipeline fixes (color matrix, preview)
  * Orientation fixes: portrait-locked preview, correct capture orientation
  * EXIF UserComment wiring for capture settings after each shot
  * Video bitrate slider and resolution picker with C++ + QML wiring
  * EIS (video stabilization) toggle
  * Top bar reorganized into two logical rows with consistent button styling
  * Resolution pickers replaced with ComboBox dropdowns
  * Defaults updated: JPEG quality 90%, neutral color correction
  * Build system: Debian packaging via distrobox container

